### Branch Service API Tests
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json
@tenantId = acme-corp
@appId = main-app
@branchId = hq-jakarta

### 1. Create Branch (Headquarters)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants/{{tenantId}}/apps/{{appId}}/branches
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "branch_id": "hq-jakarta",
  "name": "Headquarters Jakarta",
  "type": "headquarters",
  "settings": {
    "timezone": "Asia/Jakarta",
    "currency": "IDR",
    "language": "id"
  }
}

### 2. Create Regional Branch (Surabaya)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants/{{tenantId}}/apps/{{appId}}/branches
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "branch_id": "regional-surabaya",
  "name": "Regional Office Surabaya",
  "type": "regional",
  "settings": {
    "timezone": "Asia/Jakarta",
    "currency": "IDR",
    "language": "id"
  }
}

### 3. Get Branch by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants/{{tenantId}}/apps/{{appId}}/branches/{{branchId}}

### 4. Get Branch by Code
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants/{{tenantId}}/apps/{{appId}}/branches/code/hq-jakarta

### 5. List All Branches for App
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants/{{tenantId}}/apps/{{appId}}/branches

### 6. Update Branch
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants/{{tenantId}}/apps/{{appId}}/branches/{{branchId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Production Updated",
  "description": "Updated production environment",
  "settings": {
    "environment": "production",
    "debug_mode": false,
    "rate_limit": 1000
  }
}

### 7. Delete Branch
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/tenants/{{tenantId}}/apps/{{appId}}/branches/{{branchId}}
